WorldStage Newsonline– Flour Mills of Nigeria Plc, Nigeria’s leading integrated food business and agro-allied group, owners of Golden penny has issued notice of share dealing by insiders involving Paul Miyonmide Gbededo, its Group Managing Director who purchased 612,326 units at 27.75 per share which amounted to N16,992,046.5 The notice at the Nigerian Stock Exchange (NSE) signed by Umolu Joseph A.O, company secretary said the transaction took place on November 20, 2020.